{"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error CS0038\"\nms.date: 07/20/2015\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"CS0038\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"CS0038\"\nms.assetid: ed378c79-c31b-4373-adfa-ee5dd2dccc9e\n---\n# Compiler Error CS0038\nCannot access a nonstatic member of outer type 'type1' via nested type 'type2'  \n  \n A field in a class is not automatically available to a nested class. To be available to a nested class, the field must be [static](../../../csharp/language-reference/keywords/static.md). Otherwise, you must create an instance of the outer class. For more information, see [Nested Types](../../../csharp/programming-guide/classes-and-structs/nested-types.md).  \n  \n The following sample generates CS0038:  \n  \n```csharp  \n// CS0038.cs  \nclass OuterClass  \n{  \n   public int count;  \n   // try the following line instead  \n   // public static int count;  \n  \n   class InnerClass  \n   {  \n      void func()  \n      {  \n         // or, create an instance  \n         // OuterClass class_inst = new OuterClass();  \n         // int count2 = class_inst.count;  \n         int count2 = count;   // CS0038  \n      }  \n   }  \n  \n   public static void Main()  \n   {  \n   }  \n}  \n```\n","nodes":[{"pos":[4,165],"embed":true,"restype":"x-metadata","content":"title: \"Compiler Error CS0038\"\nms.date: 07/20/2015\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"CS0038\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"CS0038\"\nms.assetid: ed378c79-c31b-4373-adfa-ee5dd2dccc9e","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error CS0038","nodes":[{"pos":[0,21],"content":"Compiler Error CS0038","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error CS0038","pos":[0,21]}]}],"path":["title"],"nosxs":false}],"yml":true},{"pos":[172,193],"content":"Compiler Error CS0038","linkify":"Compiler Error CS0038","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error CS0038","pos":[0,21]}]},{"content":"Cannot access a nonstatic member of outer type 'type1' via nested type 'type2'","pos":[194,272]},{"content":"A field in a class is not automatically available to a nested class.","p